snippet.title: Rune Trailer: Flicker of Light
snippet.description:
"I have been told tales of the end of the world. A terrible war that will drown the Nine Realms in a black maelstrom of destruction and despair. Yet in the darkness - a flicker of light will finally appear." 

Updated Launch Date: Rune Will Enter Early Access This Winter Read more here:
https://www.runeragnarok.com/updated-launch-date-rune-will-enter-early-access-this-winter/
